<div class="row">
  <div class="two-thirds">
    <div class="article">
      <p>To be granted a licence, you’ll need to show you have enough money to keep your vehicles and run your business. <a href="">Read more about financial evidence</a></p>
      <h3>How much will you need?</h3>
      <h2>£12,998</h2>
      <p>This figure’s based on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>an application for 20 vehicles</li>
        <li>maintenance of 19 vehicles on your other licences</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <form>
      <h3>Send a copy to us</h3>
      <p>Once you have your financial evidence, you should either upload or post a copy to us. See the <a href="">types of evidence we accept</a>.</p><hr />
      <fieldset>
        <legend>How would you like to send your evidence?</legend>
        <div class="field inline checkbox">
          <label><input type="radio" name="evidence" value="upload">Upload files</label>
        </div>
        <div class="field inline checkbox">
          <label><input type="radio" name="evidence" value="post">Send in the post</label>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset class="js-upload">
        <fieldset class="file-uploader" id="FileUploader2">
          <ul class="attach-action__list">
            <li class="attach-action">
              <label class="attach-action__label">
                Attach file
                <input class="attach-action__input js-visually-hidden" type="file" name="fileUpload[]">
              </label>
              <p class="attach-action__hint">PDF, DOC, JPG, PNG or GIF</p>
            </li>
          </ul><!-- attach-actions -->
        </fieldset><!-- .file-uploader -->
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset class="js-post">
        <div class="article">
          <p>If you’d rather post a copy, send it as soon as possible to:<p/>
          <p>
          Office of the Traffic Commissioner<br />
          The Central Licensing Office<br />
          Hillcrest House<br />
          Leeds, LS9 6NF</p>
          <p>Make sure you include your application reference: <b>OB1523424/133</b>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
      <div class="actions-container">
        <a href="" class="action--primary large">Save and continue</a>
        <a href="" class="action--tertiary list large">Save and return to overview</a>
      </div>

    </form>

  </div>

  <div class="one-third">
    <div class="sidebar">
